race.comment: The well-related SILVER WEDDING (11) (full to G1 winner Schwarz) has been plying her trade in harder Sydney metropolitan contests this campaign and will appreciate the drop back in company here. Ready to peak now third-up from the break and maps well for Maloney from gate four. Rates the testing material. MISS BUSSLINGER (9) has been thereabouts in both runs this preparation and her only victory did come around this circuit. Must be respected from the Lees barn. CREATIVITY MISS (8) will be rock-hard fit now fourth run back and is more than capable enough on her day. In the mix on best figures. CLEAR PROOF (2) is another Sydney raider who is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley. Capable of sharp improvement. LAND BANK (4) gets the reliable Gollan/Jones combination and may earn some minor money.
